{"tid":795874,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"所有的記憶都是潮濕的","createTime":"2018-08-27T10:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T17:07:12.000Z","uid":71004,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7082d3dabb691df199af0c96c9f615a14ce534","tid":795874,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"這八月的潮濕特別叫人鬱悶，鬱悶得令四年聚散分離的故事，說說聽聽就完了。<br />\n<br />\n你不回來了，就這樣不回來了，沒帶走沉重的故事劇情離座了。<br />\n<br />\n我整理著散落四周的回憶，一簇簇海棠依舊的細節弱不禁風地填滿了可怕的空虛，那是空空如也的空，就連思想也容不下的空。<br />\n<br />\n思想是可怕的，倘若腦筋動了，活在被你遺下的回憶的我，除了為一無所有的自己不知所措外，只剩下探頭到窒息的回憶。<br />\n<br />\n在潮濕的記憶中，任我仰天長嘯，酒醒何處。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e4ba14c4142aad001e3ff55992a29550aebc01","tid":795874,"uid":204299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"清 加油 釋懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052fc4027ebc5de9f98cc41d8befd6f981de8927","tid":795874,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"文筆gd"},{"pid":"93a2d577d7ca680a09690c55e0bcae4b1a320f05","tid":795874,"uid":71004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4e4ba14c4142aad001e3ff55992a29550aebc01","tid":795874,"uid":204299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"清 加油 釋懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你 偽善撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smil